      "created_at": "2025-01-28T06:48:33.636Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi all,</p>\n<p>I have a question about the ERG mode in the app. I have an Elite Qubo Smart trainer, which is an on-wheel trainer,  and Magene cadence sensor attached to the crank. All this time I have been thinking that ERG mode is using the Magene cadence sensor to control power but yesterday I disconnected such sensor and I was still showing cadence and controlling power, which indicates that it is using my smart trainer output.<br>\nMy question is the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Is it possible to tell the app to use the external cadence sensor for ERG mode?</li>\n<li>In case it is not possible. How is then the cadence estimated by the trainer? Wheel speed is not enough to derive cadence, right?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thank you in advance.</p>",
